Package: concomp
Title: Find connected components and boundaries of the components.
Version: 0.1
Authors@R: as.person(c(
    "Dipesh Gautam <dipesh.gautam@duke.edu> [aut, cre]",
    "Radhika Anand <radhika.anand@duke.edu> [aut]",
    "Haosheng Luo <haosheng.luo@duke.edu> [aut]"))
Description: An implementation of connected components labeling in R. It identifies both
    labels and boundaries of components. Also convert png images into logical matrices
    which can be used to identify labels and boundaries.
Depends:
    R (>= 3.0.2),
    png,
    Matrix
License: None
LazyData: true